dc_title_s: Hydro (Line and Polygon) Washington County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2023. The following features are included: 'Washington_Hydro_2023_LINE' and 'Washington_Hydro_2023_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
